hololive English 2nd Concert ‐Breaking Dimensions‐ will be held at KINGS THEATRE in NYC on August 24-25, 2024!

◆OFFICIAL HASHTAG
#BreakingDimensions

◆VENUE TICKETS
Venue ticket sales will be started at 9 PM June 28th EDT.

◆STREAMING TICKETS
https://breakingdimensions.hololivepro.com/tickets/

◆CONCERT MERCH

https://breakingdimensions.hololivepro.com/
